Enum HttpStatusCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<HttpStatusCode>
      • de.esoco.lib.comm.http.HttpStatusCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<HttpStatusCode>

    public enum HttpStatusCode
extends java.lang.Enum<HttpStatusCode>
    An enumeration of the standard HTTP 1.1 status codes as defined in the HTTP RFC 2616.
